    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is ready for its next adventure with you! It's perfect for daily commutes or those fun weekend road trips. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
