    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a quintessential analog performer featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution during corner exit. The chassis remains taut, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already performed and the suspension geometry maintained for sharp turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are strong, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a crisp exhaust note free of rasp. An excellent opportunity for a purist seeking a visceral driving experience without the premium of a collector-grade garage queen.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
