    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been taken care of so well. It\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself how much fun it is to drive!",
